With that, I ended the call.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
It was a strange feeling.[l][r]
It's scary yet warm, adorable yet sad. [l][r]
As those indescribable emotions calmed down, the Yuri in my mind finally lowered his gun and smiled, a little sadly. [l][r]

[r]I search for the rest of the words that had crossed my mind a moment ago. Yes, those kids are... [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

